          #sex.section
            -var accent_color = "rgb(220,48,138)"
            br
            h2 Sex
            p An overwhelming majority of student respondents, 91%, believe in the existence of a hookup culture at Andover, and 38.3% of all respondents have felt pressured to participate in the hookup culture. 49% of respondents have engaged in sexual activity, compared to 52% from last year’s survey. 37 respondents have been sexually assaulted on campus, 91 off campus, and 28 both on and off campus. 33 respondents have been sexually harassed on campus, 208 off campus, and 125 both on and off campus. 66% of respondents believe that the current sexual education curriculum at Andover is adequate.
            br
            include sections/sex.pug
            br
